类 AbstractRocksDBState<K,N,S extends State,SD extends StateDescriptor<S,V>,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.contrib.streaming.state.AbstractRocksDBState<K,N,S,SD,V>
  • 类型参数:
    K - The type of the key.
    N - The type of the namespace.
    S - The type of State.
    SD - The type of StateDescriptor.
    所有已实现的接口:
    State, InternalKvState<N>
    直接已知子类:
    RocksDBAggregatingState, RocksDBFoldingState, RocksDBListState, RocksDBMapState, RocksDBReducingState, RocksDBValueState

    public abstract class AbstractRocksDBState<K,N,S extends State,SD extends StateDescriptor<S,V>,V>
extends java.lang.Object
implements InternalKvState<N>, State
    Base class for State implementations that store state in a RocksDB database.

    State is not stored in this class but in the RocksDB instance that the RocksDBStateBackend manages and checkpoints.
